1st. Blind guy played by Ayushman struggles to complete his music , he was being crazy creative artist can do anything for the greatness.

Akash reaches his home first he plays some old bollywood music and after that he plays his own incomplete music which the things gets interesting he starts imagining what if Pramod was murdered by his wife(he starts relating music with a story), now he is  completely lost in his music, he could relate and play his music into thriller ,mystery and he is the part of that story .
All the characters are real but he uses as a fictional,
Police,Lottery lady, autowala , doctor,boy . He starts using them in his music/story.
 He finds the key to his music ,  the beginning and the conclusion.(3rd part )

This is also supplemented by the fact that the rabbit in the movie was also blind by one eye. Thus the rabbit actually symbolised Ayushman's character in the movie. An incredible metaphor which went unnoticed by many.
